{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·005.1", "text_original": "旻天疾威，敷于下土，謀猶回遹，何日斯沮？\n謀臧不從，不臧覆用。我視謀猶，亦孔之卭。", "text_normalized": "旻天疾威，敷于下土，謀猶回遹，何日斯沮？\n謀臧不從，不臧覆用。我視謀猶，亦孔之卭。", "notes": "小旻 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·005.2", "text_original": "潝潝訿訿，亦孔之哀。謀之其臧，則具是違。\n謀之不臧，則具是依。我視謀猶，伊于胡厎？", "text_normalized": "潝潝訿訿，亦孔之哀。謀之其臧，則具是違。\n謀之不臧，則具是依。我視謀猶，伊于胡厎？", "notes": "小旻 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·005.3", "text_original": "我龜既厭，不我告猶。謀夫孔多，是用不集。\n發言盈庭，誰敢執其咎？如匪行邁謀，是用不得于道。", "text_normalized": "我龜既厭，不我告猶。謀夫孔多，是用不集。\n發言盈庭，誰敢執其咎？如匪行邁謀，是用不得于道。", "notes": "小旻 Chinese stanza 3."}
